<item>
            <title>[LU-11880] Allow Lustre build on Raspbian and other Debian derivatives</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11880</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Allow Lustre &lt;tt&gt;.deb&lt;/tt&gt; packages to be built on Rasbian and other Debian-based derivatives.  Instead of keying off the distro name, check if &lt;tt&gt;dpkg&lt;/tt&gt; is installed to determine if &lt;tt&gt;.deb&lt;/tt&gt; packages can be built.  Add support for the &lt;tt&gt;armhf&lt;/tt&gt; architecture.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
